Safaricom has launched a new customer reward campaign to boost the usage of the Lipa Na M-Pesa service for retail purchases. The Lipa Na M-Pesa Cash Back Promotion, which will run for the next two months, will see users who meet their weekly target receive cash rewards ranging from Sh5 to Sh100. ALSO READ:

Telkom Kenya launches mobile money service “Customers will now have the opportunity to get some money back once they hit their targets,” said Rita Okuthe, director enterprise business, in a statement Monday.